  "displayTitle": "<span class=\"mw-page-title-main\">Pure Brilliance</span>",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p><i>Exclusive to:</i> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve_Together\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together\"><img alt=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png/32px-Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png?3bc208\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a><br>\n</p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p><b>Pure Brilliance</b> is a resource exclusive to <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve_Together\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together\">Don&#x27;t Starve Together</a></i>, introduced in <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/From_Beyond\" title=\"From Beyond\">From Beyond</a></i>. It is obtained by mining <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ryftstal\" title=\"Ryftstal\">Ryftstals</a> that spawn from <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Lunar_Rift\" title=\"Lunar Rift\">Lunar Rifts</a>.\n</p><p>Pure Brilliance is used to craft the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Brightsmithy\" title=\"Brightsmithy\">Brightsmithy</a> and all of the items craftable at said station.\n</p><p><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wilson/Don%27t_Starve_Together\" title=\"Wilson/Don&#x27;t Starve Together\">Wilson</a> with the <span class=\"dark-invert\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Lunar_Innovator\" title=\"Lunar Innovator\"><img alt=\"Lunar Innovator.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Lunar_Innovator.png/24px-Lunar_Innovator.png?300f2d\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\"></a></span> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Lunar_Innovator\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Lunar Innovator\">Lunar Innovator</a> Skill can craft 1 Pure Brilliance with 3 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Infused_Moon_Shard\" title=\"Infused Moon Shard\">Infused Moon Shards</a>, as well as use 1 Pure Brilliance to craft 2 Infused Moon Shards. \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Usage\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Icon_Tools\" title=\"Icon Tools\"><img alt=\"Icon Tools.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Icon_Tools.png/32px-Icon_Tools.png?f672d4\" width=\"32\" height=\"39\"></a> Usage</span></h2>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Pure_Brilliance\" title=\"Pure Brilliance\"><img alt=\"Pure Brilliance.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Pure_Brilliance.png?102a2c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Moon_Shard\" title=\"Moon Shard\"><img alt=\"Moon Shard.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Moon_Shard.png?50cae4\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>5</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Moon_Rock\" title=\"Moon Rock\"><img alt=\"Moon Rock.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Moon_Rock.png?189e68\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>5</b></p></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Celestial_Altar\" title=\"Celestial Altar\"><img alt=\"Celestial Altar.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Celestial_Altar.png/42px-Celestial_Altar.png?6223d1\" width=\"42\" height=\"62\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Brightsmithy_Kit\" title=\"Brightsmithy Kit\"><img alt=\"Brightsmithy Kit.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Brightsmithy_Kit.png?ccff22\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Pure_Brilliance\" title=\"Pure Brilliance\"><img alt=\"Pure Brilliance.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Pure_Brilliance.png?102a2c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>4</b></p></td><td><div class=\