_arrow_right.png/42px-Interface_arrow_right.png?d3cbb3\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Luminous_Wrath\" title=\"Luminous Wrath\"><img alt=\"Luminous Wrath.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Luminous_Wrath.png?721283\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wendy\" title=\"Wendy\"><img alt=\"Wendy Portrait.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Wendy_Portrait.png/64px-Wendy_Portrait.png?de6a98\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></td><td class=\"dark-invert\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Lunar_Sisterhood_II\" title=\"Lunar Sisterhood II\"><img alt=\"Lunar Sisterhood II.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Lunar_Sisterhood_II.png?8dc9d1\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Trivia\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Placeholder\" title=\"Placeholder\"><img alt=\"Placeholder.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Placeholder.png/32px-Placeholder.png?210282\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Trivia</span></h2>\n<ul><li>Pure Brilliance was introduced in the <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/From_Beyond#Taking_Root\" title=\"From Beyond\">Taking Root</a></i> update.</li>\n<li>The opposite of this item is <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Pure_Horror\" title=\"Pure Horror\">Pure Horror</a>.</li>\n<li>Pure Brilliance is a play on words as the word Brilliance pertains to both high intelligence and intense luminescence.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Assets\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Research_Notes\" title=\"Research Notes\"><img alt=\"Research Notes.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Research_Notes.png/32px-Research_Notes.png?ef2da4\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Assets</span></h2>\n<ul class=\"gallery mw-gallery-traditional\">\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Pure_Brilliance_Dropped_Idle.gif\" class=\"image\" title=\"Idle animation\"><img alt=\"Idle animation\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Pure_Brilliance_Dropped_Idle.gif/120px-Pure_Brilliance_Dropped_Idle.gif?6be614\" width=\"120\" height=\"119\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">Idle animation</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"tabber tabber--init\"><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"Resources-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Pure_Brilliance#Resources-0\">Resources</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"Craftable_Items-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Pure_Brilliance#Craftable_Items-0\">Craftable Items</a><section class=\"tabber__section\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></section></div>\n\n\n\n\n</div>",
