  "wikitext": "{{Object Infobox\n|craft_desctiption =Transmute Infused Moon Shards into Pure Brilliance.\n|name=Pure Brilliance\n|icon = Pure Brilliance.png\n|image = Pure Brilliance Dropped.png\n|spawnCode=\"purebrilliance\"\n|filter={{Pic32|Wilson Filter}}\n|stack=40\n|ingredient1=Infused Moon Shard\n|multiplier1=3 ({{Pic|28|Wilson Portrait|Wilson}} only)\n|droppedBy={{pic32|Ryftstal}}{{pic32|Armored Bearger}}{{pic32|Crystal Deerclops}}{{pic32|Possessed Varg}}{{pic32|Celestial Scion}}{{pic32|Inimical Gestalt}}\n|skill = Lunar Innovator\n|skillOwner = Wilson\n}}\n{{Exclusivity|Don't Starve Together}}\n{{Quotes\n|wilson = It's blinding me with science!\n|willow = It's pretty, but it'll never beat fire.\n|wolfgang = Little rocks are too bright!\n|wendy = It hurts my eyes.\n|wx78 = IT IS... PERFECTION...\n|wickerbottom = Pure energy, in a crystalline form.\n|woodie = Makes me feel a bit twitchy.\n|maxwell = I wonder if she knows about this...\n|wigfrid = Like staring up intö the spötlights...\n|webber = It's blinding our poor spider eyes!\n|warly = My, I've never seen anything shine so brightly.\n|wormwood = Ahhh. Pretty.\n|winona = I ain't dazzled by much, but that'll do it.\n|wortox = Hyuyu, it tickles my impish brain!\n|wurt = Glurgh, too bright!\n|walter = That's gotta be the shiniest rock I've ever seen.\n|wanda = If only I could use it to power one of my watches... Oh well.\n|choose = wx78\n}}\n\n'''Pure Brilliance''' is a resource exclusive to ''[[Don't Starve Together]]'', introduced in ''[[From Beyond]]''. It is obtained by mining [[Ryftstal]]s that spawn from [[Lunar Rift]]s.\n\nPure Brilliance is used to craft the [[Brightsmithy]] and all of the items craftable at said station.\n\n[[Wilson/Don't Starve Together|Wilson]] with the {{picDark|24|Lunar Innovator}} [[Lunar Innovator]] Skill can craft 1 Pure Brilliance with 3 [[Infused Moon Shard]]s, as well as use 1 Pure Brilliance to craft 2 Infused Moon Shards. \n\n=={{pic|32|Icon Tools}} Usage== \n{{Recipe\n|item3 = Moon Rock\n|count3 = 5\n|item2 = Moon Shard\n|count2 = 5\n|item1 = Pure Brilliance\n|count1 = 1\n|result = Brightsmithy Kit\n|tool = Celestial Altar\n}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item2 = Brightshade Husk\n|count2 = 4\n|item1 = Pure Brilliance\n|count1 = 4\n|result = Brightshade Armor\n|tool = Brightsmithy}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item2 = Brightshade Husk\n|count2 = 2\n|item1 = Pure Brilliance\n|count1 = 4\n|result = Brightshade Helm\n|tool = Brightsmithy}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item2 = Brightshade Husk\n|count2 = 4\n|item1 = Pure Brilliance\n|count1 = 4\n|item3 = Infused Moon Shard\n|count3 = 1\n|result = Brightshade Bomb\n|tool = Brightsmithy\n|resultcount = 6}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item2 = Brightshade Husk\n|count2 = 6\n|item1 = Pure Brilliance\n|count1 = 3\n|result = Brightshade Staff\n|tool = Brightsmithy}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item2 = Brightshade Husk\n|count2 = 3\n|item1 = Pure Brilliance\n|count1 = 4\n|result = Brightshade Sword\n|tool = Brightsmithy}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item2 = Brightshade Husk\n|count2 = 2\n|item1 = Pure Brilliance\n|count1 = 1\n|result = Brightshade Smasher\n|tool = Brightsmithy}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item2 = Brightshade Husk\n|count2 = 2\n|item1 = Pure Brilliance\n|count1 = 1\n|result = Brightshade Shoevel\n|tool = Brightsmithy}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item2 = Brightshade Husk\n|count2 = 1\n|item1 = Pure Brilliance\n|count1 = 1\n|result = Brightshade Repair Kit\n|tool = Brightsmithy}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item3 = Cut Grass\n|count3 = 3\n|item2 = Boards\n|item1 = Pure Brilliance\n|result = Bright Boxer\n|tool = Prestihatitator}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|tool = Brightsmithy\n|item3 = Spark Ark\n|item2 = Thick Fur\n|item1 = Pure Brilliance\n|count1 = 3\n|item4 = Moon Rock\n|count4 = 5\n|result = Polar Bearger Bin\n}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|tool = Brightsmithy\n|item3 = Spark Ark\n|item2 = Moon Shard\n|count2 = 8\n|item1 = Pure Brilliance\n|count1 = 3\n|item4 = Moon Rock\n|count4 = 5\n|result= Ice Crystaleyezer Kit\n}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|tool = Brightsmithy\n|item3 = Spark Ark\n|item2 = Brightshade Husk\n|count2 = 3\n|item1= Pure Brilliance\n|count1= 3\n|item4 = Moon Rock\n|count4 = 3\n|result= Howlitzer\n}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|tool = blueprint_(rare)\n|item3= Enlightened Shard\n|count3= 1\n|item1= Pure Brilliance\n|count1= 2\n|item2= Scrap\n|count2= 4\n|result= Elastispacer\n}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Pure Brilliance\n|count1 = 1\n|result = Infused Moon Shard\n|character = Wilson\n|skill = Lunar Innovator\n|resultcount = 2}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Pure Brilliance\n|tool = Brightsmithy\n|result = Pure Brilliance Rounds\n|character = Walter\n|skill = Lunar Slinger\n|resultcount = 20}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Pure Brilliance\n|item2 = Driftwood Piece\n|item3 = Marsh Turf\n|result = Brilliant Mudslinger\n|character = Wurt\n|skill = Terra Mutation\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Pure Brilliance\n|item2 = Mourning Glory\n|count2 = 3\n|result = Luminous Wrath\n|character = Wendy\n|skill = Lunar Sisterhood II\n}}\n\n== {{pic|32|Placeholder}} Trivia ==\n* Pure Brilliance was introduced in the ''[[From Beyond#Taking Root|Taking Root]]'' update.\n* The opposite of this item is [[Pure Horror]].\n* Pure Brilliance is a play on words as the word Brilliance pertains to both high intelligence and intense luminescence.  \n== {{Pic32|Research Notes}} Assets ==\n<gallery>\nPure Brilliance Dropped Idle.gif|Idle animation\n</gallery>\n<tabber>\nResources=\n{{Resources}}\n|-|\nCraftable Items=\n{{Craftable Items and Structures on DST}}\n</tabber>\n[[Category:From Beyond]]\n[[vi:Pure Brilliance]]\n[[zh:纯粹辉煌]]"
